{
  "stem": "232.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we were walked in this way here, where the quarantine camp was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The quarantine camps, I don't know why they kept the prisoners separate for four weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They shouldn't be sick or give any sickness to other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Here, they were burning women and children and men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And here, the-- the opposite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They try to keep the inmates healthy from people who maybe have any sickness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, we-- we arrived in a block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A block is a barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, all inmates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started calling in Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I found out a little while later, they called out the numbers to distribute food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And most of the inmates here where Polish people, who talk Polish to-- to the-- to inmates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they called my number, I didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, I, of course, I didn't go forward to collect my food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was waiting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when everybody got their food, and I still was standing there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I ask as I went forward to the blockalteste, who is the-- the responsible person for this barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, where's my food?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he started shouting to me and give me a kick in the butt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I ran because I don't want to get to another one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I started to-- to ask somebody if he understand German or French, that's the language I was speaking, to teach me my number in Polish so that I don't lose any move food.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because this food was very important to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What kind of food it was?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the evening, they gave you a three-quarter like water and there were some beets swimming around.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
